WEBVTT

00:01:42.039 --> 00:01:43.199
You are Ye Biying, right?

00:01:43.800 --> 00:01:45.080
You are Ye Biying, right?

00:01:50.280 --> 00:01:51.120
What are you doing?

00:01:51.839 --> 00:01:52.559
Let go of me!

00:01:55.039 --> 00:01:55.839
Let go of me!

00:02:00.239 --> 00:02:02.920
Shut up! Behave!

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:09.679
Stop that!

00:02:10.759 --> 00:02:11.759
What are you doing?

00:02:12.560 --> 00:02:13.520
Let her go!

00:02:26.520 --> 00:02:27.280
Father!

00:02:37.840 --> 00:02:38.680
Ying'er!

00:02:39.719 --> 00:02:40.519
Father!

00:02:47.840 --> 00:02:49.439
Why have you come back?

00:02:53.519 --> 00:02:55.799
Why come back in the middle of this chaos?

00:03:01.879 --> 00:03:02.680
She is my daughter.

00:03:02.680 --> 00:03:03.799
Why are you arresting her?

00:03:05.879 --> 00:03:07.760
We have some questions for her.

00:03:07.760 --> 00:03:08.959
She is my daughter.

00:03:08.959 --> 00:03:10.799
What's wrong with coming back to her own home?

00:03:12.719 --> 00:03:14.879
Do you know who you're talking to?

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:19.040
What?

00:03:19.040 --> 00:03:19.719
Wait.

00:03:19.719 --> 00:03:20.400
I'm sorry.

00:03:20.400 --> 00:03:21.000
Listen to me.

00:03:21.079 --> 00:03:21.599
I've always warned you.

00:03:21.599 --> 00:03:22.719
Don't act so impulsively.

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:24.599
Don't be so impulsive.

00:03:24.599 --> 00:03:25.280
Get out!

00:03:32.599 --> 00:03:33.319
Mr. Ye.

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:35.040
Calm down.

00:03:35.319 --> 00:03:36.000
I'm truly sorry.

00:03:36.959 --> 00:03:37.760
She is my daughter.

00:03:37.760 --> 00:03:38.479
Why are you arresting her?

00:03:38.479 --> 00:03:39.400
Yes, yes, yes.

00:03:39.560 --> 00:03:40.319
She is your daughter.

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:40.759
Right?

00:03:40.879 --> 00:03:42.439
We just found out ourselves.

00:03:42.919 --> 00:03:44.000
Untie her quickly.

00:03:44.479 --> 00:03:45.479
Quickly!

00:03:45.479 --> 00:03:46.400
Untie her.

00:03:51.400 --> 00:03:51.960
Alright.

00:03:52.159 --> 00:03:53.039
It's okay.

00:03:53.039 --> 00:03:53.520
It's okay.

00:03:53.639 --> 00:03:54.560
Father will protect you.

00:03:55.599 --> 00:03:55.960
Come.

00:03:56.199 --> 00:03:56.639
Let's go.

00:03:58.719 --> 00:03:59.360
Please wait.

00:04:00.199 --> 00:04:01.280
Mr. Ye.

00:04:01.759 --> 00:04:04.960
We still have one more matter to investigate.

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:05.879
Investigate what?

00:04:07.639 --> 00:04:08.360
It's this.

00:04:08.960 --> 00:04:09.879
This suitcase.

00:04:10.520 --> 00:04:11.520
We discovered it.

00:04:12.439 --> 00:04:14.080
We believe it's hers.

00:04:15.080 --> 00:04:15.759
And then?

00:04:16.120 --> 00:04:17.439
Inside this...

00:04:17.520 --> 00:04:19.319
There is a pistol.

00:04:25.639 --> 00:04:26.759
Is the gun yours?

00:04:31.960 --> 00:04:32.719
It's not hers.

00:04:33.319 --> 00:04:34.639
I know my daughter.

00:04:35.159 --> 00:04:36.199
We can leave now, right?

00:04:38.159 --> 00:04:38.599
Fine.

00:04:42.439 --> 00:04:43.240
Miss Ye.

00:04:43.759 --> 00:04:44.520
Your foot.

00:04:45.639 --> 00:04:47.639
The area around here is all mountain roads.

00:04:47.639 --> 00:04:48.680
It's too dangerous like this.

00:04:49.199 --> 00:04:49.639
Have a seat.

00:04:49.639 --> 00:04:50.400
Sit, sit, sit.

00:04:50.439 --> 00:04:51.000
Sit, sit, sit.

00:04:51.000 --> 00:04:51.479
Have a seat.

00:04:51.520 --> 00:04:52.080
Sit.

00:04:52.240 --> 00:04:52.599
Sit.

00:04:55.240 --> 00:04:55.800
You see.

00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:57.879
You can't go out like this.

00:04:57.879 --> 00:04:59.360
You could easily get hurt.

00:05:10.840 --> 00:05:13.520
May I borrow your esteemed foot?

00:05:25.879 --> 00:05:27.439
It fits perfectly.

00:05:31.439 --> 00:05:34.439
Where did this pistol come from?

00:05:43.080 --> 00:05:44.280
Your occupation.

00:05:45.479 --> 00:05:48.439
I was a dance hostess at a ballroom in Shanghai.

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:49.399
Is that so?

00:05:52.279 --> 00:05:55.560
That's a good profession these days.

00:05:57.839 --> 00:05:59.199
You worked at the...

00:05:59.199 --> 00:06:01.680
Cathay Ballroom on Edward Road as a dance hostess.

00:06:03.240 --> 00:06:04.600
I've been to that ballroom.

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:05.839
The lighting is nice.

00:06:06.439 --> 00:06:11.000
It's just that the marble dance floor is a bit too slippery.

00:06:12.319 --> 00:06:13.120
Right?

00:06:21.959 --> 00:06:23.439
Medhurst Road.

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:25.360
I didn't hear clearly.

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:26.000
What?

00:06:26.199 --> 00:06:26.680
You say it.

00:06:29.759 --> 00:06:33.639
The Cathay Ballroom is on Medhurst Road.

00:06:34.959 --> 00:06:37.079
Not where you said.

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:38.959
Furthermore...

00:06:40.759 --> 00:06:42.439
It has a sprung dance floor.

00:06:43.439 --> 00:06:45.040
Not marble.

00:06:48.160 --> 00:06:48.879
Yes.

00:06:50.279 --> 00:06:52.360
I left Shanghai three or four years ago.

00:06:52.800 --> 00:06:54.160
No wonder I mixed things up.

00:06:54.720 --> 00:06:55.800
Back then...

00:06:55.800 --> 00:06:58.399
We would all start from the barracks in Hongkou.

00:06:58.720 --> 00:07:00.680
First take the number 26 tram.

00:07:00.680 --> 00:07:01.959
First to Beihai Road.

00:07:02.120 --> 00:07:05.600
Then pass by Park Lane to get to your ballroom.

00:07:06.040 --> 00:07:07.279
At the entrance of Park Lane...

00:07:07.279 --> 00:07:09.680
There was also a Xieji Snack Shop.

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:12.839
Their food was really delicious.

00:07:13.959 --> 00:07:14.959
Now tell me.

00:07:16.040 --> 00:07:17.279
What is your mission?

00:07:17.279 --> 00:07:18.480
Who sent you in?

00:07:18.480 --> 00:07:19.720
Let her go! Let her go!

00:07:20.800 --> 00:07:22.079
Whether my daughter is a dance hostess...

00:07:22.399 --> 00:07:23.399
Is none of your business.

00:07:23.439 --> 00:07:24.360
I'll handle it myself.

00:07:25.639 --> 00:07:26.199
Let's go.

00:07:27.480 --> 00:07:28.480
Mr. Ye.

00:07:29.639 --> 00:07:30.639
Do you think...

00:07:32.839 --> 00:07:35.199
Your relationship with Commander Fujita...

00:07:35.879 --> 00:07:37.639
Can protect her?

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:42.600
I protect my daughter.

00:07:43.680 --> 00:07:44.959
I don't rely on anyone.

00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:53.720
Xia'er!

00:07:56.439 --> 00:07:57.319
Xia'er!

00:07:58.279 --> 00:07:58.720
Nanny!

00:07:58.759 --> 00:07:59.279
It's terrible!

00:07:59.680 --> 00:08:00.279
It's terrible!

00:08:00.519 --> 00:08:01.879
The master has been taken to the police station.

00:08:01.959 --> 00:08:03.360
The Japanese have arrested him.

00:08:03.639 --> 00:08:03.920
Let's go.

00:08:04.199 --> 00:08:04.680
Go and see.

00:08:13.079 --> 00:08:13.720
What are you doing?

00:08:15.319 --> 00:08:16.199
Listen up, everyone!

00:08:16.720 --> 00:08:17.759
Search the place!

00:08:18.079 --> 00:08:18.600
Yes, sir!

00:08:28.360 --> 00:08:29.160
What are you doing?

00:08:33.519 --> 00:08:34.399
Ye Longxia!

00:08:43.360 --> 00:08:44.160
Captain!

00:08:44.759 --> 00:08:47.120
What do you want? I'm busy!

00:08:47.480 --> 00:08:50.920
An officer has barged in.

00:09:00.600 --> 00:09:01.480
Mr. Ye.

00:09:01.920 --> 00:09:02.920
My name is Takeki Ichiro.

00:09:03.199 --> 00:09:03.839
Pleased to meet you.

00:09:04.040 --> 00:09:04.879
I look forward to working with you.

00:09:09.319 --> 00:09:10.720
It's only been a few hours since I left you.

00:09:11.480 --> 00:09:12.879
And you've gotten yourself into such a mess.

00:09:15.600 --> 00:09:16.800
Your shirt buttons are all undone.

00:09:17.560 --> 00:09:18.399
Who undid them?

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:32.839
Button up your shirt.

00:09:39.040 --> 00:09:39.920
You did it.

00:09:41.439 --> 00:09:41.959
Did she not tell you

00:09:41.959 --> 00:09:42.680
that she is my woman?

00:09:43.800 --> 00:09:44.199
Speak.

00:09:45.240 --> 00:09:46.120
Wait a moment.

00:09:46.120 --> 00:09:46.800
We found this in that woman's bag.

00:09:46.800 --> 00:09:47.879
You shut your mouth.

00:09:50.040 --> 00:09:53.439
May I ask who you are?

00:09:54.480 --> 00:09:55.920
This is the special envoy sent from Tokyo.

00:09:55.920 --> 00:09:58.920
Colonel Takeki Ichiro of the Imperial Aide-de-Camp Office.

00:10:02.200 --> 00:10:03.080
Salute!

00:10:04.559 --> 00:10:05.320
Order arms!

00:10:09.759 --> 00:10:10.639
Captain Inoue, is it?

00:10:10.720 --> 00:10:11.039
Yes.

00:10:11.559 --> 00:10:12.039
I've long heard of you.

00:10:13.559 --> 00:10:14.759
When I was in Shanghai,

00:10:14.759 --> 00:10:17.039
your father, Mr. Inoue Akira, and I

00:10:17.039 --> 00:10:17.960
along with Miss Ye

00:10:17.960 --> 00:10:19.720
drank together at the Cathay Dance Hall.

00:10:22.360 --> 00:10:24.200
Miss Ye is my assistant.

00:10:24.200 --> 00:10:25.440
She is under my protection.

00:10:25.440 --> 00:10:28.120
The gun in your hand was given to her by me.

00:10:36.000 --> 00:10:36.919
Keep the gun safe.

00:10:37.639 --> 00:10:38.759
If you encounter danger,

00:10:39.279 --> 00:10:40.480
you may fire directly.

00:10:42.879 --> 00:10:43.720
Colonel.

00:10:43.720 --> 00:10:45.039
The Commander is still waiting for us.

00:10:48.200 --> 00:10:49.840
May Miss Ye go home now?

00:10:50.159 --> 00:10:51.519
Of course. This way, please.

00:10:52.240 --> 00:10:52.840
Mr. Ye, please.

00:10:58.360 --> 00:10:59.039
Wait.

00:10:59.639 --> 00:11:00.200
This bag...

00:11:00.200 --> 00:11:00.879
Give it to me.

00:11:01.519 --> 00:11:01.919
Yes.

00:11:03.399 --> 00:11:03.879
Captain Inoue.

00:11:03.879 --> 00:11:04.240
Yes.

00:11:04.519 --> 00:11:05.600
Transportation on the island is inconvenient.

00:11:05.600 --> 00:11:06.759
I need a vehicle.

00:11:07.200 --> 00:11:07.679
Understood.

00:11:07.679 --> 00:11:10.159
I will prepare a vehicle and driver for the Colonel immediately.

00:11:10.159 --> 00:11:11.679
Yes, understood.

00:11:11.679 --> 00:11:12.480
A driver will not be necessary.

00:11:12.480 --> 00:11:13.879
Alright, no driver.

00:11:13.879 --> 00:11:14.840
My apologies for the offense.

00:11:19.240 --> 00:11:20.360
Thank you. Farewell.

00:11:33.679 --> 00:11:34.279
Father.

00:11:34.840 --> 00:11:35.519
Father.

00:11:38.639 --> 00:11:39.720
I understand.

00:11:41.679 --> 00:11:42.639
Who is he?

00:11:45.080 --> 00:11:46.960
His name is Takeki Ichiro.

00:11:48.320 --> 00:11:49.159
A Japanese.

00:11:54.440 --> 00:11:54.840
Dad.

00:11:55.399 --> 00:11:56.080
Biying.

00:11:59.120 --> 00:12:00.080
Put the luggage in my car for now.

00:12:00.080 --> 00:12:01.519
The other gun is with Luo Zhiyong.

00:12:01.639 --> 00:12:02.759
I'll go see my father first.

00:12:03.960 --> 00:12:04.399
Dad.

00:12:09.200 --> 00:12:09.840
Colonel.

00:12:10.080 --> 00:12:11.600
Commander Fujita is still waiting for you.

00:12:12.159 --> 00:12:12.480
Please.

00:12:24.240 --> 00:12:26.440
Has Sasaki returned yet?

00:12:28.120 --> 00:12:28.799
Right.

00:12:29.559 --> 00:12:30.320
He hasn't returned yet.

00:12:33.519 --> 00:12:34.440
Right.

00:12:35.919 --> 00:12:37.039
He's probably still in Tanjiawan Village.

00:12:37.039 --> 00:12:38.279
Searching the secret room.

00:12:38.279 --> 00:12:39.879
Should we send someone to tell him to come back immediately?

00:12:40.399 --> 00:12:41.440
Go ahead.

00:12:43.279 --> 00:12:43.759
Come back.

00:12:46.399 --> 00:12:49.240
Don't bother. Let him search.

00:12:52.759 --> 00:12:54.559
If Sasaki doesn't find anyone,

00:12:54.840 --> 00:12:56.879
and this Colonel complains to the Commander about it,

00:12:56.919 --> 00:12:58.720
I'm afraid headquarters will blame us.

00:12:58.720 --> 00:13:00.279
What's there to panic about?

00:13:00.279 --> 00:13:02.440
While this Colonel from the palace

00:13:02.440 --> 00:13:03.519
is meeting with Commander Fujita,

00:13:03.519 --> 00:13:05.559
we'll raid the Ye family's nest.

00:13:05.559 --> 00:13:07.000
Seize the initiative.

00:13:07.000 --> 00:13:11.159
This is our Special Police Corps' job.

00:13:11.200 --> 00:13:12.440
What did you just say?

00:13:12.919 --> 00:13:15.960
You dare say we haven't caught anyone?

00:13:16.039 --> 00:13:16.600
Let me tell you,

00:13:16.600 --> 00:13:17.360
if we really haven't caught anyone,

00:13:17.360 --> 00:13:18.039
but if we do find someone,

00:13:18.080 --> 00:13:18.799
I'd like to see how this Colonel

00:13:18.799 --> 00:13:19.639
and that woman of his from the Ye family

00:13:19.639 --> 00:13:22.120
can still act so arrogantly.

00:13:22.120 --> 00:13:25.279
This is our Special Police Corps' job.

00:13:50.720 --> 00:13:51.960
Search thoroughly for me.

00:13:51.960 --> 00:13:53.200
Don't overlook any place.

00:13:53.200 --> 00:13:54.000
Yes!

00:14:07.600 --> 00:14:08.600
All men, prepare!

00:14:08.720 --> 00:14:09.759
Prepare!

00:14:09.879 --> 00:14:11.240
The greatest threat to you

00:14:11.240 --> 00:14:13.120
is this Lieutenant General Fujita.

00:14:13.240 --> 00:14:15.399
He enjoys Japanese historical texts

00:14:15.600 --> 00:14:17.000
and also Chinese history.

00:14:17.159 --> 00:14:18.399
He's a China expert.

00:14:18.759 --> 00:14:19.360
This man served as

00:14:19.360 --> 00:14:21.440
an assistant military attachÃ© at the New York consulate.

00:14:21.639 --> 00:14:24.279
He's a rare historian within the Japanese Navy.

00:14:24.480 --> 00:14:25.720
He is very deep and calculating.

00:14:26.159 --> 00:14:28.120
If he sends a telegram to verify your identity,

00:14:28.320 --> 00:14:29.480
then the time until your exposure

00:14:29.679 --> 00:14:31.559
generally will not exceed forty-eight hours.

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:33.440
You may consider aborting the mission

00:14:33.639 --> 00:14:34.639
and extracting immediately.

00:14:52.960 --> 00:14:54.320
Investigator of the Imperial Palace Investigation Office,

00:14:54.440 --> 00:14:55.600
Takeki Ichiro,

00:14:55.600 --> 00:14:56.879
presents himself to Commander Fujita.

00:14:59.159 --> 00:15:02.600
It's a pleasure to meet you here.

00:15:04.320 --> 00:15:05.000
Sakamoto.

00:15:05.240 --> 00:15:05.639
Yes.

00:15:09.360 --> 00:15:10.559
I am Adjutant Sakamoto.

00:15:10.559 --> 00:15:11.200
We have already received

00:15:11.200 --> 00:15:12.279
notification from the Shanghai garrison.

00:15:12.279 --> 00:15:13.559
We have been waiting for you here for some time.

00:15:15.919 --> 00:15:17.320
Commander, you must be tired.

00:15:27.320 --> 00:15:29.200
An envoy from the palace.

00:15:29.600 --> 00:15:30.399
The purpose of your trip

00:15:30.399 --> 00:15:32.200
must be quite extraordinary.

00:15:34.879 --> 00:15:35.440
Come.

00:15:35.840 --> 00:15:36.559
This way, please.

00:15:52.679 --> 00:15:54.679
Even if you don't wish to say, I can guess.

00:15:54.799 --> 00:15:56.799
It's probably about the Osumi Mineo matter.

00:15:57.159 --> 00:15:57.600
In recent years,

00:15:57.600 --> 00:15:58.679
the only thing here that could alarm the palace

00:15:58.759 --> 00:16:00.039
is this one matter.

00:16:01.159 --> 00:16:02.159
Commander.

00:16:02.440 --> 00:16:03.360
I believe Adjutant Sakamoto

00:16:03.360 --> 00:16:04.360
will certainly be able to find me

00:16:04.360 --> 00:16:05.639
a comfortable place to rest.

00:16:07.080 --> 00:16:07.759
Right.

00:16:08.320 --> 00:16:08.879
Sakamoto.

00:16:09.000 --> 00:16:09.360
Yes.

00:16:09.360 --> 00:16:10.720
Go immediately and make arrangements for the envoy.

00:16:10.919 --> 00:16:11.919
Have the envoy stay at the headquarters.

00:16:11.919 --> 00:16:13.200
Being closer to me will facilitate communication.

00:16:13.320 --> 00:16:14.200
Commander.

00:16:14.679 --> 00:16:16.399
I think I'd prefer to stay at the airfield.

00:16:16.440 --> 00:16:17.279
The airfield garrison

00:16:17.279 --> 00:16:18.600
and all the pilots are stationed there.

00:16:18.840 --> 00:16:19.720
It will be more convenient for my work.

00:16:22.200 --> 00:16:23.120
I understand.

00:16:23.919 --> 00:16:25.320
Have the airfield garrison

00:16:25.320 --> 00:16:26.639
vacate a better quarters for the envoy's use.

00:16:26.639 --> 00:16:29.320
All provisions are to be according to my standard.

00:16:29.320 --> 00:16:30.200
Understood.

00:16:31.639 --> 00:16:32.480
Then let us go inside first.

00:16:32.480 --> 00:16:33.159
Yes.

00:16:48.080 --> 00:16:48.679
Salute.

00:16:49.440 --> 00:16:50.279
This way, please.

00:16:50.279 --> 00:16:50.879
Very well.

00:16:57.600 --> 00:16:58.320
Colonel, please have a seat.

00:16:58.320 --> 00:16:58.840
Yes.

00:17:06.720 --> 00:17:07.519
Sit.

00:17:07.519 --> 00:17:08.080
Good.

00:17:18.120 --> 00:17:20.200
Commander Fujita, I have one more thing to report.

00:17:20.200 --> 00:17:21.840
The Colonel is one of us.

00:17:22.600 --> 00:17:23.440
Go ahead.

00:17:24.720 --> 00:17:26.639
Ye Degong has a letter for you.

00:17:50.840 --> 00:17:53.279
I heard you studied at the To Bun Gakuin.

00:17:53.279 --> 00:17:54.720
So you must be able to read Chinese.

00:17:54.720 --> 00:17:56.279
Yes, I understand some.

00:18:09.159 --> 00:18:09.720
Sakamoto.

00:18:10.080 --> 00:18:10.679
Yes.

00:18:10.679 --> 00:18:12.639
Has the Special Police Corps taken any action recently?

00:18:13.279 --> 00:18:14.440
They suspect...

00:18:14.679 --> 00:18:15.679
...that on the downed plane...

00:18:15.679 --> 00:18:17.600
...there might have been another American.

00:18:17.600 --> 00:18:20.559
But this person has never been found.

00:18:20.600 --> 00:18:21.960
The Special Police Corps searched Tanjiawan Village...

00:18:21.960 --> 00:18:23.360
...and every other village on the island.

00:18:33.120 --> 00:18:34.039
Colonel...

00:18:34.240 --> 00:18:35.880
How do you think such a matter should be handled?

00:18:36.359 --> 00:18:36.960
Your Excellency...

00:18:37.119 --> 00:18:38.319
I have just arrived on the island.

