00:36:02.119 --> 00:36:03.519
I'd like to hear your view.

00:36:04.079 --> 00:36:05.039
Commander, sir.

00:36:05.039 --> 00:36:07.800
Do you want to hear the view consistent with newspapers and documents,

00:36:07.840 --> 00:36:09.960
or my personal view?

00:36:09.960 --> 00:36:12.719
Of course, it's the private view between you and me.

00:36:13.840 --> 00:36:14.360
Yes.

00:36:20.800 --> 00:36:25.280
It will increase greatly.

00:36:25.960 --> 00:36:30.199
You think this Colonel Takeki also has problems?

00:36:30.719 --> 00:36:31.840
I don't know if he has problems.

00:36:32.840 --> 00:36:33.559
I just remembered

00:36:35.159 --> 00:36:37.039
my psychology when playing cards.

00:36:40.719 --> 00:36:41.480
What psychology?

00:36:42.159 --> 00:36:45.039
When I'm holding a bad hand,

00:36:45.880 --> 00:36:47.639
I will bluff,

00:36:48.079 --> 00:36:53.119
pretending to be overbearing,

00:36:53.119 --> 00:36:54.920
completely intending to fool my opponent.

00:36:58.280 --> 00:36:59.000
You mean

00:36:59.000 --> 00:37:00.400
Colonel Takeki's credentials are problematic?

00:37:01.159 --> 00:37:02.280
I only know that

00:37:02.280 --> 00:37:05.239
if this person is holding a good hand...

00:37:05.239 --> 00:37:06.719
What kind of hand is this?

00:37:06.719 --> 00:37:07.480
He will definitely give his opponent a feeling

00:37:07.480 --> 00:37:08.480
of having bad luck.

00:37:08.480 --> 00:37:10.039
He often hides

00:37:10.039 --> 00:37:12.559
his truest feelings and confidence.

00:37:18.599 --> 00:37:20.760
Should we investigate Colonel Takeki?

00:37:24.320 --> 00:37:25.840
How?

00:37:26.440 --> 00:37:27.360
We can't very well

00:37:27.360 --> 00:37:30.360
send a telegram to His Majesty the Emperor and the Prime Minister

00:37:30.360 --> 00:37:32.880
to verify their investigator's identity, can we?

00:37:33.599 --> 00:37:34.719
Then we can't do anything about him.

00:37:34.719 --> 00:37:36.320
Even if we

00:37:37.159 --> 00:37:38.920
can't telegraph the Emperor and Prime Minister...

00:37:38.920 --> 00:37:40.320
Therefore, we can start investigating from that woman.

00:37:41.519 --> 00:37:43.519
Start from the woman?

00:37:43.519 --> 00:37:44.119
Yes.

00:37:46.719 --> 00:37:48.760
The Pearl River Estuary here is like spring all year round.

00:37:48.760 --> 00:37:50.440
It's truly a good place.

00:37:50.440 --> 00:37:54.320
The base has fresh fruit all year round.

00:37:55.199 --> 00:37:56.000
Please, enjoy.

00:37:56.000 --> 00:37:56.400
Good.

00:37:59.000 --> 00:37:59.719
Thank you.

00:38:06.920 --> 00:38:07.800
It's truly delicious.

00:38:11.199 --> 00:38:12.000
Commander.

00:38:12.800 --> 00:38:13.679
In my humble opinion,

00:38:13.920 --> 00:38:15.440
the naval strength of the United States

00:38:15.440 --> 00:38:17.280
is superior to our own naval strength.

00:38:18.000 --> 00:38:18.559
Although we

00:38:18.559 --> 00:38:20.000
launched a surprise attack on Pearl Harbor

00:38:20.000 --> 00:38:21.480
and essentially destroyed

00:38:21.480 --> 00:38:22.719
the U.S. Pacific Fleet,

00:38:22.719 --> 00:38:23.840
this has made the officers of the Southern Expansion Faction

00:38:23.840 --> 00:38:24.880
somewhat overconfident.

00:38:24.880 --> 00:38:27.000
They think American naval power is nothing special.

00:38:28.960 --> 00:38:31.519
Many admirals in the navy do not share this view.

00:38:32.119 --> 00:38:33.639
The United States has formally declared war on us.

00:38:34.159 --> 00:38:35.280
Our Kwantung Army

00:38:35.280 --> 00:38:36.800
has fourteen divisions,

00:38:36.800 --> 00:38:38.639
over 1.3 million men,

00:38:38.800 --> 00:38:40.639
yet we dare not transfer a single division

00:38:40.639 --> 00:38:42.679
to join the southern campaign.

00:38:43.000 --> 00:38:44.880
We can only continuously conscript from the homeland.

00:38:45.559 --> 00:38:46.719
Just before I came here,

00:38:46.719 --> 00:38:48.360
a new conscription order was issued.

00:38:48.360 --> 00:38:49.880
The upper age limit for conscription

00:38:49.880 --> 00:38:51.440
has now reached fifty-five.

00:38:53.320 --> 00:38:54.559
Indeed.

00:38:54.559 --> 00:38:56.400
This matter is enough to worry His Majesty.

00:38:56.400 --> 00:38:58.119
Our entire homeland defense now

00:38:58.119 --> 00:38:59.760
consists of only three divisions.

00:38:59.760 --> 00:39:02.280
The rest are useless reservists.

00:39:02.280 --> 00:39:04.920
If any unforeseen situation arises,

00:39:04.920 --> 00:39:06.920
I fear there will be major trouble.

00:39:09.119 --> 00:39:11.440
Truly worthy of being by His Majesty's side.

00:39:11.440 --> 00:39:13.239
Your perspective on matters is indeed different.

00:39:16.280 --> 00:39:17.480
Our attack on Pearl Harbor

00:39:17.920 --> 00:39:19.199
has thoroughly enraged America.

00:39:19.880 --> 00:39:20.719
It is a massive

00:39:20.719 --> 00:39:24.639
combined naval, land, and air combat force.

00:39:24.639 --> 00:39:26.159
America's industrial capacity

00:39:26.159 --> 00:39:27.960
far exceeds our own.

00:39:27.960 --> 00:39:29.840
Imagine two years from now,

00:39:29.840 --> 00:39:32.239
our army's artillery and navy's ships

00:39:32.239 --> 00:39:33.559
are continuously lost in battle and cannot be replaced.

00:39:33.559 --> 00:39:34.880
But American factories,

00:39:34.880 --> 00:39:36.280
running at full capacity,

00:39:36.280 --> 00:39:37.840
produce new artillery and new ships,

00:39:37.840 --> 00:39:39.679
creating new troubles.

00:39:39.679 --> 00:39:40.679
By that time,

00:39:40.920 --> 00:39:42.559
I truly dare not imagine

00:39:42.559 --> 00:39:44.360
what situation we will face.

00:39:47.920 --> 00:39:49.440
The Naval General Staff has done something

00:39:49.920 --> 00:39:51.199
that made Roosevelt, Churchill,

00:39:51.199 --> 00:39:51.800
and China's Chiang Kai-shek

00:39:51.800 --> 00:39:52.800
all very happy.

00:39:54.159 --> 00:39:54.960
Last month, I met

00:39:54.960 --> 00:39:56.119
Admiral Isoroku Yamamoto.

00:39:56.559 --> 00:39:58.079
His concerns are the same as yours.

00:39:58.400 --> 00:40:00.159
Truly worthy of being a staff officer at Supreme Headquarters.

00:40:00.719 --> 00:40:01.760
Your vision is indeed broad.

00:40:01.760 --> 00:40:02.800
It's truly different.

00:40:04.320 --> 00:40:05.159
Only by swiftly completing

00:40:05.159 --> 00:40:05.960
operations across the entire China theater,

00:40:06.599 --> 00:40:08.119
and transferring all main forces here

00:40:08.119 --> 00:40:09.280
to the Pacific battlefield,

00:40:10.079 --> 00:40:11.239
can we ensure that two years from now,

00:40:11.239 --> 00:40:12.800
the Japanese homeland remains safe.

00:40:19.320 --> 00:40:21.280
Pardon me, sir.

00:40:21.719 --> 00:40:22.719
Following your instructions,

00:40:22.719 --> 00:40:23.400
I went to invite Ye Degong.

00:40:23.400 --> 00:40:24.199
But he refused.

00:40:26.079 --> 00:40:30.000
Also, the Special Police Corps has withdrawn.

00:40:30.840 --> 00:40:31.599
I understand.

00:40:32.280 --> 00:40:32.760
You may leave.

00:40:33.039 --> 00:40:33.360
Yes.

00:40:33.599 --> 00:40:34.559
I take my leave.

00:40:35.159 --> 00:40:36.559
This must be the interpreter, Mr. Luo.

00:40:37.800 --> 00:40:38.480
My female assistant.

00:40:38.480 --> 00:40:40.039
And there is something in your possession.

00:40:42.280 --> 00:40:44.000
So you are Colonel Takeki.

00:40:47.000 --> 00:40:49.280
I've long intended to return this to you in person.

00:40:49.280 --> 00:40:50.480
I simply forgot for a moment.

00:40:56.639 --> 00:40:57.960
Thank you for keeping it for her.

00:41:00.719 --> 00:41:02.840
If Colonel Takeki hadn't mentioned it,

00:41:03.480 --> 00:41:04.719
you probably wouldn't have returned it voluntarily.

00:41:05.400 --> 00:41:06.039
Commander.

00:41:06.320 --> 00:41:07.239
I truly wouldn't dare.

00:41:09.360 --> 00:41:10.400
Bring that here.

00:41:10.760 --> 00:41:11.000
Yes.

00:41:12.760 --> 00:41:13.480
The noble man is open and at ease.

00:41:13.480 --> 00:41:14.679
The petty man is always full of anxiety.

00:41:17.440 --> 00:41:19.199
Swat fifty flies.

00:41:19.960 --> 00:41:21.880
Arrange them neatly.

00:41:23.280 --> 00:41:24.079
After I finish my discussion with the Colonel,

00:41:24.079 --> 00:41:25.000
I will personally come to inspect.

00:41:25.320 --> 00:41:25.559
Yes.

00:41:26.239 --> 00:41:26.559
Get out.

00:41:27.000 --> 00:41:27.280
Yes.

00:41:36.519 --> 00:41:38.400
He is a fly

00:41:38.840 --> 00:41:39.920
that has infiltrated our army.

00:41:40.280 --> 00:41:40.639
Yes.

00:41:41.719 --> 00:41:42.320
Sakamoto.

00:41:42.519 --> 00:41:42.679
Yes.

00:41:43.079 --> 00:41:44.400
There's one more thing I'd like to ask of you.

00:41:44.719 --> 00:41:45.639
Please go to my car

00:41:45.639 --> 00:41:47.119
and fetch a green cloth bag.

00:41:47.480 --> 00:41:48.159
As you command.

00:41:48.159 --> 00:41:48.760
Thank you.

